message: Human trafficking is not just an international problem but also a domestic issue, and local efforts to help everyday people recognize the problem can be what it takes to save a victim, said Chad Hahn, victim advocate for YWCA Northcentral PA, a city-based organization that promises support for victims of domestic, violent and sexual abuse.
